# Privacy Policy

## Introduction
Welcome to RiseMedia. This privacy policy explains how RiseMedia handles user information and data when you use our games. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.

## Information We Collect
### 1. Information Automatically Collected
- **RiseMedia Data:** We use RiseMedia to serve advertisements in our games. RiseMedia may collect data about your device and your interaction with ads. RiseMedia does not store this data.

## How We Use Information
- **Ad Serving:** The information collected by RiseMedia is used to serve personalized advertisements within our games. This helps us keep our games free to play and provide a better user experience.

## Third-Party Services
### RiseMedia
- **RiseMedia:** We integrate RiseMedia to display ads in our games. RiseMedia may collect and use data . This may include device information, ad performance metrics, and user interactions with ads.

## Your Choices
- **Ad Preferences:** You can manage your ad preferences and opt out of personalized ads through your device settings.

## Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect the information that is processed on our behalf by RiseMedia. However, please be aware that no method of transmitting information over the internet or storing information is completely secure.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within our games or on our website. Your continued use of our games after any changes indicates your acceptance of the new privacy policy.

## Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at: suraj.bakawat@risemediatech.io

Thank you for playing our games.
